{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "段玉奉父命携祖传碧玉刀赶往宝珠山庄，为朱二太爷拜寿并完成两家婚约。段飞熊反复告诫他江湖六戒，段玉却初入江湖便遇上花夜来，被美色与偷盗牵入麻烦，又结识机敏的华华凤。碧玉刀、宝珠山庄和花夜来的出现，把他的求亲之行推入一场更大的阴谋。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是我积几十年经验得来的教训，你一定要牢记在心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "麻婆豆腐",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "善酿",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奎元馆",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在路上千万不可和陌生的女人打交道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位兄台请了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的兄台，就是阁下。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是跟你说话是跟谁说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却不知阁下有何见教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刷",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下当然也看得出我不是。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是谁是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在江湖中最不能惹的，就是和尚、道士和乞丐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是出家人，还是强盗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是那女子的什么人？要来管这闲事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天下人管天下事，这闲事我为何管不得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "救命呀，救命，这些凶僧要行非礼。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你们这些和尚的胆子倒真不小。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的胆子也不小，竟敢在洒家面前如此放肆！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "施主高姓？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我姓段。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段玉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段施主好武功。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马马虎虎，还过得去。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "施主难道看不出贫僧等是从什么地方来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噗通",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段公子，请留步。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必……在下很好。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子你本来就是个好人，我知道。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是这个意思，我是说，我没有病。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有病就更好了，船上还有一坛陈年的竹叶青……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必，不必客气，在下正要告辞。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子的酒钱，我……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行，不必客气，我这里有。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段公子，段玉，玉郎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎呀，可怜的小伙子，他为什么要贪睡呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花姑娘，花夜来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你起来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些东西本来就不是她的，要还也不能还给她呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道石家客栈在哪边？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你渡我过去，我给你十两银子。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看我像是个强盗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若不是强盗，怎么会渡一次湖就给十两银子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你嫌多？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本来嫌多的，现在却嫌少了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的银子既然来得容易，要坐我的船，就得多给些。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你身上有多少，我就要多少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 772
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来我不是强盗，你才是强盗。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在才知道，已经太迟了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这真是条贼船？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听说贼船上若要杀人时，通常有两种法子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 784,
      "line_end": 784
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道的事倒真不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 786
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却不知你是想请我吃板刀面呢，还是要把我包馄饨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那就得看你的银子是不是给得痛快了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 790
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "善财难舍，要拿银子给人，怎么能痛快得起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 792,
      "line_end": 792
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么看来我只好先请你下去洗个澡。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不用客气，我刚洗过。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在水还很冷，洗澡当心要着凉。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然是好轻功。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 830
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马马虎虎还过得去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 832,
      "line_end": 832
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你不学好，还是我不学好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 838,
      "line_end": 838
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等一等。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 850,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我忘了谢谢你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 854
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢谢我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 856,
      "line_end": 856
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管你说的话是真是假，我一样还是要谢谢你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不想死。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 866,
      "line_end": 866
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我活得好好的，你为什么总是说我快要死了呢？",
