      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 878,
      "line_end": 878
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的是那四个大和尚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 880,
      "line_end": 880
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是不是我的运气已渐渐变坏了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 890,
      "line_end": 890
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你回来，我们话还没有说完。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 892,
      "line_end": 892
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有什么话没说完？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 894,
      "line_end": 894
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你肯带我到凤林寺去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 916,
      "line_end": 916
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不带你到凤林寺去，难道带你去死。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 918,
      "line_end": 918
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "千万不可和陌生的女人打交道，千万不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 920,
      "line_end": 920
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那船家叫你来找一个姓顾的道人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 954,
      "line_end": 954
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 956,
      "line_end": 956
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没有听错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 958,
      "line_end": 958
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我耳朵还没有毛病。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 960,
      "line_end": 960
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昨天我打下水的那四个和尚，莫非就是凤林寺的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 966,
      "line_end": 966
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看不出你倒也是行家。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
